Package fi.tuni.tamk.tiko.tiko2a

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndroidLauncher  
    BundleHandler
    This is our games asset manager.
    Drawing
    This class handles rendering what the player draws, the objective circles, checking if player is drawing close enough to the lines and checking if the player has cleared the obstacle.
    Fade
    This class is used to make a background colored texture that fills the whole screen.
    Goal
    This class is used to show the goal screen.
    HUD
    The HUD class for our screen, this is in use at the transition and drawing screens.
    newMainMenu
    This is the MAIN MENU class, we load into this when the game starts.
    Obstacle
    This Class handles the Obstacles.
    Play1
    This class is the screen where the player chooses how (s)he feels like.
    Play2
    This class is the screen where the player chooses how (s)he feels like.
    Player
    This class handles the creation of the player animation
    PlayMain
    This class is used to show the player what he chose on the Play1 and Play2 screens.
    Prefs
    This class handles our saved data.
    Resultscreen
    This class is used to show the screen AFTER player has drawn a successful draw-screen.
    Settings
    Settings Screen class for our game, is currently only used to change the volume of the background music..
    Sounds
    This class is for handling all the sounds and music of the game.
    Transition
    This class is used to show the Transition screen.
    Utils  
    zenSpace
    Pelin pohjaluokka, täällä luodaan kaikki asiat, mitä käytetään muissa luokissa Spritebatchi, kamerat, fontit, ym.
